{
  "stem": "27390.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because the Jewish police, they-- they kept you away from the fence.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Even if you managed to do a deal with a German guard or something, the Jewish police was in the way.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "See, they were-- they--, how shall I say?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very determined to see that nobody escapes because I think he had to report-- if there was one or two people missing, he had to produce either the body or the person.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If a-- every day people died.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had to produce the bodies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "See, there was a check up, how many bodies the, the, they buried in the-- in the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody could escape from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, so they started then picking-- if the people didn't report, so they started picking the people from the, from the, from the houses, from the apartments.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we lived in-- the ghetto, I didn't mention this, was divided into three parts.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--picture later.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The ghetto was this divided into three parts.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And every part, in order to cross from one part into the other, you had to cross over was a bridge.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So what they done is, in order to isolate the part where we lived, they gave an order that whoever is found tomorrow in this part will be shot on sight.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we hid for a day or two, but it was getting too risky because there weren't many people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were deporting all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we crossed over into the other part of the ghetto where my-- my uncle wasn't alive anymore-- where his children lived in that room where originally we came in the beginning when we were taken out from our apartment.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we came in to this room.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
